casebody.data:
In the Matter of Neal Gerace, Respondent, v. F. Wilson Smith et al., Appellants, and Charles F. Furst et al., as Commissioners of Election of Rockland County, Respondents. Argued May 27, 1964; decided May 27, 1964. Leon H. Klingher for appellants. George S. Cobb for Neal Gerace, respondent.

No appearance for remaining respondents.

Order reversed and prayer of the petition denied, without costs (see Matter of Lamula v. Power, 13 N Y 2d 873).

Concur: Chief Judge Desmond and Judges Dye, Fuld, Van Voorhis, Burke, Scileppi and Hamm*.
